description:
YOU'VE BEEN LOOKING AT ME... AND YOU'RE GOING TO PAY FOR IT!
Jessa has invited you over to her house. You are not sure what to expect, but when you get there she informs you that, she has noticed you constantly watching her. She knows you are married to your fat rich wife. She makes it very clear that unless You PAY HER FOR EVERY TIME YOU LOOK AT HER, she is going to inform your wife. She makes sure you get a long hard look at what you can't have... She records you looking. She then tells you you owe her even more money. In fact, you are going to buy this video from her!
title: Cold & Beautiful... She Is the Most Wicked Fin Dom Alive
